{"tid":998761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英婦貪刺激同鄰居換夫 成個家都換埋","createTime":"2019-01-28T08:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T08:19:01.000Z","uid":1735,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de89da8c443654c4e2da1ca37e12fe825950fa4f","tid":998761,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:01:21.000Z","msg":"一失足成千古恨！英國現年78歲的婦人莫里亞蒂(Kay Moriarty)原本一家四口生活美滿，但40多年前貪一時激情，與鄰居好友麗達(Rita)玩換夫，從此就人生大逆轉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuX3DGg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuX3DGg.png&h=5023b7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時的莫里亞蒂<br />\n<br />\n莫里亞蒂憶述，她19歲嫁給丈夫羅拔，從未出軌，但夫妻生活逐漸枯燥，她便渴望遇上一夜情，羅拔初時不肯，但麗達的丈夫泰利卻躍躍欲試，4人便決定「玩吓」，想不到原來是噩夢開始。那次之後，麗達竟與羅拔互生情愫，還說想一對子女與他們同住，莫里亞蒂晴天霹靂，但又對娘家羞於啟齒，唯有「啞子吃黃蓮」，被迫與泰利一起，同居後才發現對方債台高築且佔有慾強，苦忍7年後決定分手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yonGqmE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyonGqmE.png&h=ae53080e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年輕的莫里亞蒂<br />\n<br />\n驀然回首，莫里亞蒂說悔不當初，現與女兒相依為命，與兒子卻關係疏離，女兒亦與生父羅拔形同陌路。她慨嘆當年玩換夫遊戲是一生的最大錯誤，雖然她不愛羅拔，卻令一對子女失掉家庭溫暖、姊弟分離。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPyFFVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPyFFVB.png&h=85aa522a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與羅拔的結婚照"},{"pid":"e281dbf461a479ce38f7c756a80aef87678f227c","tid":998761,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:01:33.000Z","msg":"Source am730"},{"pid":"9eb44c66403a71bd7540e82045ac5dd8a46793da","tid":998761,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"雙方NTR"},{"pid":"ecb555e33ec74a1eb2a2afd17b749e4fb56f6b2a","tid":998761,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:04:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1edbfd958a8409ffbcaa049e44a636c85b8ac552","tid":998761,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"對家條佬咁衰<br />\n<br />\n佢原老婆緊係出盡討好換夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n千載難逢機會"},{"pid":"b9fd634cb7d3770e03eb9e53d6d90900945770fc","tid":998761,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1edbfd958a8409ffbcaa049e44a636c85b8ac552","tid":998761,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"對家條佬咁衰<br />\n<br />\n佢原老婆緊係出盡討好換夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n千載難逢機會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"無頭東宮互換老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb2d5b49eb7084a1c0a989fc908ae1754c6a8bd","tid":998761,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f02e6a2d277dad1f29c5ea96f0d93f26074126","tid":998761,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:19:01.000Z","msg":"無頭東宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}